Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.39,0:00:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上鞋子敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.03,0:00:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.47,0:01:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.35,0:01:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十話 希望你聆聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河的水準就是不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她願意加入聲樂社嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只讓她代打太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱得真好呢，琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿分、滿分、滿分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（距離園遊會只剩三天）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家別只動嘴巴，動動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是芳乃櫻獨家設計\N美國道地的運動咖啡廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為風紀委員的我\N不容許妳們如此暴露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責取締的怎麼能跟著起鬨啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.79,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉也留下來準備園遊會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是假裝的，不過也膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我琴梨就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼琴梨，妳在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在音樂教室練習園遊會的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是聲樂社的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有加入聲樂社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.73,0:03:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為我有參加唱詩班\N所以他們常找我去代唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:03:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有厲害啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.18,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都得當風紀委員～\N美春和音夢學姊快煩死囉～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.73,0:04:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就來放學還得加班\N美春已經快累斃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園遊會時風紀委員是最忙碌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩兩天而已，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特製的巧克力香蕉鯛魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個我就能會努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃到腦漿都快溶化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.66,0:05:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來最近忙到\N都沒時間和哥哥聊天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊\N這就是所謂的作息不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聊的話題越變越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離婚、贍養費、監護權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時還是跟美乃商量比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的情報還真是偏頗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得一起來吃早餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也一大早就起來辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家特地做的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是超商的便當就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暖桌要配橘子、牛(03)要配紅薑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選美要有美麗的花朵登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.21,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為何要我請琴梨參加選美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你跟白河琴梨很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交情好到會一起回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張票要給誰好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是要給妳哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被發現啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.73,0:06:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為小美超喜歡哥哥的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杉並的情報網真恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕他的話事情會被亂傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會有無中生有的謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白河琴梨，好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想參加她的發表會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純粹只是想聽我唱歌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣會很勉強你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.28,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒參加社團\N當天也沒被強迫做工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我時間多得是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我哪說得出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要我請她參加選美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杉並那傢伙居然逼我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學很為難呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力香蕉鯛魚燒，上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，音夢學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是朝倉學長和白河學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有一起吃飯了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.08,0:08:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，最近也很少聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，在學校裡有聊到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思\N是指我們兩人單獨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒時間陪我\N卻有空陪白河學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.97,0:08:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然看到就打聲招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕打擾到你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為杉並拜託我\N請白河去參加選美的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過白河會答應真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選美…我也參加好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.19,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最恐怖的鬼屋就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怨恨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女生好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是個鬼耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是擺這種攤位喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去那邊巡視一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那美春就往這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.64,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.48,0:09:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢竟然說要參加選美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都特地請我吃東西了\N抱歉我卻幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，妳吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.23,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊有說過\N最近幾乎都碰不到朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得一起來吃早餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近也很少聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個可以到那邊的招待處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來探班，沒有特別的含意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外到讓我有點吃驚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓妳更加意外一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，妳有休息時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到時候逛一逛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟最近很少跟妳聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這也沒有特別的含意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兩點在教室見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.43,0:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間竟然衝到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家排成兩行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像在遊樂園玩過之後\N要回家寫作業一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換做是我就不寫功課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了，美春還在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能開心就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就帶點東西去看琴梨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發表會不是取消了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盛況空前剛剛才結束呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是琴梨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河她說取消啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽錯了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有參加所以絕對沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.93,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風見學園小姐由白河琴梨當選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟音夢約的時間\N跟琴梨發表會的時間衝到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼這麼糊塗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要選哪邊比較好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.34,0:13:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情怎麼能用選的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.89,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點事情\N所以發表會取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時也只能那麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是好想唱給朝倉同學聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.01,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治癒內心翅膀的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.86,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在櫻花樹下相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.67,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的一刻溫暖我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.55,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以呼喚我最珍惜的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風的呢喃使我露出微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.11,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望總有一天能傳達這份心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.57,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發表會取消是我弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為我太緊張吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.71,0:15:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別介意，這樣的結果對我剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能知道對方的想法有時是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學很疼妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎，這可是新的學說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好只是他的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告\N雖然能看到別人的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想傳達自己的心意卻好難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候琴梨可以唱歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次是要說賴子出門的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴子至今都沒有出門過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不敢出門去買東西\N這可是不及格的女僕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是愛的鞭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼愛啊？\N（第十一話  出門去吧！ ）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.96,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.27,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於鈴音輕響的樹蔭下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子\N高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨紛飛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.76,0:17:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛總是能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在釣魚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.60,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的氣候很好\N所以有很多魚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.10,0:21:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以釣到很大的魚，敬請期待
